Title: New Order (1)
Plot: Carter and Teal'c go in search of the Asgard to try and save Colonel O'Neill, but discover that the Asgard's enemy has returned with a vengeance. The System Lords seek an alliance with Earth against a common enemy.
GuestStars: G. Patrick Currie, Torri Higginson, Steve Bacic, Kira Clavell, Kevan Ohtsji, Barclay Hope, Chelah Horsdal, Todd Masters, Adam Behr, Geoff Redknap, Paul Hoosen, Jeny Cassady, Brad Proctor
